1
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:19,640
This Li Xingyao cannot be used.

2
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:20,480
We must replace her.

3
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:26,680
This is what Wang Rui sent me.

4
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:27,960
Old Zhou,

5
00:00:28,840 --> 00:00:29,680
tell me the truth.

6
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:31,360
Did you organize this talent show

7
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,320
because of her?

8
00:00:33,720 --> 00:00:35,520
A singer who can't sing on stage —

9
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:36,840
why would I sign her?

10
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:38,480
Teacher Zhou,

11
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,960
our Tiantian entrusted her first live stream concert to you,

12
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:43,880
supporting a newcomer is based on absolute trust in you.

13
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,440
But if the person you chose

14
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:47,320
can't even hold the most basic stage,

15
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:49,160
then we cannot gamble Tiantian's future

16
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:50,400
on your personal feelings.

17
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,480
We're still in the rehearsal stage.

18
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,360
he hasn't even gone on stage yet.

19
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,520
Isn't it too early to say these things?

20
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,120
If rehearsal is like this,

21
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,800
will the actual performance be okay?

22
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,360
And that lousy mask —

23
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,000
Will he wear it like that during the live stream too?

24
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,880
With so many audience members down there,

25
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,960
What will you do if he can't sing?

26
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:55,320
This is Tiantian's first solo live stream concert.

27
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,760
If he messes it up,

28
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,680
the company, Tiantian, the efforts of all of us —

29
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,520
everything will be ruined.

30
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:05,360
I have no problem.

31
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,000
I trust Old Zhou.

32
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:11,560
Thank you.

33
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,440
It's just rehearsal.

34
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,520
Who doesn't get stage fright as a newcomer?

35
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:18,680
He'll get better with practice.

36
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,480
I'm not as carefree as you.

37
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,520
Old Zhou,

38
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,080
I need your word.

39
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:28,160
Can you guarantee that when he goes on stage,

40
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,240
no problems will arise?

41
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,520
If something goes wrong,

42
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,880
can you take responsibility?

43
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:36,360
I will not take responsibility for things that haven't happened yet.

44
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,200
Calm down, Old Cui.

45
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:43,720
Wait until he really can't sing during the official selection

46
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:47,000
before you lose your temper. That'll be soon enough.

47
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,440
Drink slowly, don't choke.

48
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,080
This is as much as I can help you.

49
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,040
I won't be the only judge then.

50
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,520
If he still —

51
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:02,760
then I'll —

52
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:03,840
OK
ok

53
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,080
I know.

54
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,480
How come I feel

55
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,600
you're not quite right?

56
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,160
What's wrong?

57
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,040
Nothing.

58
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:32,520
Your little boyfriend got wronged,

59
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,760
feeling sorry for him?

60
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,360
What?

61
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,080
You two aren't together?

62
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:45,680
No.

63
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,200
Sooner or later.

64
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,280
Why would you think that?

65
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,320
Because

66
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,200
only when you look at him,

67
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,680
your eyes are passionate.

68
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,240
You are the one who pushed away.

69
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,800
Why are you blaming me?

70
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,160
Because

71
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,200
only when you look at him,

72
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,520
your eyes are passionate.

73
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,480
I'm sorry.

74
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,400
I still messed up.

75
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,880
You've helped me so much,

76
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,680
and I still can't sing.

77
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,200
Are you disappointed in me?

78
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,320
It's okay, Xiaoyao.

79
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,880
You were almost there.

80
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,280
As soon as there are people around me,

81
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:07,600
those voices come back to my ears.

82
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,760
We cannot run away from fear.

83
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,520
We must face it.

84
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,240
The farther you hide,

85
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,560
the closer it chases you.

86
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:19,760
What about you?

87
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,920
That day's events —

88
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,280
you remember everything,

89
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,440
don't you?

90
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,320
You said you blacked out from drinking,

91
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:35,800
but you remember.

92
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,600
I like you.

93
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,800
Not as a friend,

94
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,240
not as a neighbor,

95
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,240
not as a brother.

96
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,160
It's "like,"

97
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,240
it's love.

98
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,320
It has been since a long time ago.

99
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,400
Do you like me?

100
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,160
I don't know.

101
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,160
Where are you going?

102
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,880
To a place where I can't see you every day.

103
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,400
What do you mean by that?

104
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:32,160
Because I can't act as if nothing happened.

105
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:35,600
I can't accept you acting like everything is fine every day,

106
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,920
being hot and cold.

107
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,120
As long as you're by my side,

108
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:42,160
I can't control myself.

109
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,440
I can't control my feelings.

110
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,760
Maybe you can,

111
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:50,680
but I —

112
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,480
can't.

113
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,400
I confessed to him.

114
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:43,040
I thought he liked me,

115
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:45,600
but his reaction —

116
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:51,840
Did I do something wrong?

117
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,600
Liking someone,

118
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,280
wanting them to know —

119
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,120
what's wrong with that?

120
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,840
He's already done enough for me,

121
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:02,760
but I still want more.

122
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,320
Xiu Jie,

123
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,240
do you think I'm too greedy?

124
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,160
Maybe

125
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,040
liking someone

126
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:15,080
just makes you unavoidably greedy.

127
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:20,720
With me,

128
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,000
you've never been greedy.

129
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,880
He probably never wants to see me again.

130
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,960
Give him a little more time.

131
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,280
People often

132
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:42,240
don't know themselves as well as they think.

133
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,000
Xiao Yao, you should become a singer in the future.

134
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,760
Do you think I can do it?

135
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:42,760
Of course.

136
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,080
Your singing has a way

137
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:46,320
of making people enter another world,

138
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:49,360
a pure world without disturbances.

139
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,360
It's so pretty.

140
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,280
My mother made it.

141
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,880
She said this pattern can bring me good luck.

142
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,000
When I learn how to make one,

143
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,160
I'll make one for you too.

144
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,960
My name is Zhou Jing'an.

145
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,080
Don't worry.

146
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:07,000
I will protect you from now on.

147
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,040
How are you here?

148
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,040
I was looking for you.

149
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,400
I went to every place you might be.

150
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,240
Xiao Yao, I'm sorry.

151
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,160
I shouldn't have treated you that way.

152
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,440
I just —

153
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,640
I'm just a little confused.

154
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,520
I know that you are

155
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,280
the most special and important person to me.

156
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,560
Precisely because of that,

157
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:52,120
I have to desperately suppress my instincts.

158
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,120
But I won't hide anymore.

159
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,160
I will seriously —

160
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:03,680
seriously see and think clearly.

161
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,640
Will you wait for me a little longer?

162
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:30,920
Xiao Yao,

163
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,800
stay by my side and don't run away again.

164
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,720
but,I can't go through

165
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,280
the pain of losing you again.

166
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,760
Why did it stop?

167
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,000
What's wrong?

168
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,240
Then you all leave first.

169
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:22,920
What the hell.

170
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,120
Don't be afraid, Xiao Yao.

171
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:52,440
Can you hear

172
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:55,080
the cicadas chirping in the alley?

173
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,520
Do you remember that smell?

174
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,080
The afternoon sun

175
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:01,720
on the old brick wall.

176
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,440
Go back to that place,

177
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,200
only to that place.

178
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:11,800
Twinkle, twinkle, little star,

179
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:15,080
The sky is full of little stars.

180
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:18,080
Hanging in the sky, shining bright,

181
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:21,000
like many little eyes.

182
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:23,920
Twinkle, twinkle, little star,

183
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:26,800
the sky is full of little stars.

184
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:29,840
Hanging in the sky, shining bright,

185
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:32,760
like many little eyes.

186
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:40,040
Then take that feeling

187
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:41,920
and sing it out.

188
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,520
Forget where you are,

189
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,160
forget who is watching you.

190
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:47,760
Not bad at all.

191
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:48,560
This time it's good.

192
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:53,680
Really good.

193
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:09,520
Xiao Yao,

194
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:11,360
you did it.

195
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:12,400
You really did it.

196
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:14,880
I really did it.

197
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,600
A little hard to believe.

198
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:19,800
You know what?

199
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,340
You, on stage,

200
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:22,600
shine.

201
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:29,000
I'm really proud of you.

202
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:40,560
Are the backstage lights off?

203
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,000
I'll go check.

204
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:48,560
Xiao Yao,

205
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,240
let's go on a date.

206
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:00,840
Hmm
